  - m_Id: 704224020647936
    m_Localized: Ziel
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 704224863703040
    m_Localized: '- Drag and drop a <STICKER> to any <BALL> enhance it. Each <BALL>
      can hold <MAX_STICKER>, default 4.

      - Bought <STICKER> appear on the
      right.

      - To sell one, click it in inventory and confirm.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 704225606094848
    m_Localized: '- Hold <LMB> to take aim and increase shoot power. Release to shoot.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 704226352680960
    m_Localized: Sticker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 704227103461376
    m_Localized: '- Complete all 8 <LEAGUE> to <WIN>.

      - Each <LEAGUE> has
      3 pools; <SMALL>, <BIG>, <PREMIUM>

      - <PREMIUM> has some negative effects

      -
      To complete a <POOL>, you have to pass its <TARGET_SCORE>

      - You can
      <SKIP> <SMALL> or <BIG> to get extra reward'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 704227866824704
    m_Localized: '- <RELICW> gives you passive bonuses during your game.

      -
      Once you purchase a <RELICW>, you can see them on bottom of your table.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 704229376774144
    m_Localized: '- You can cancel powering with <RMB>'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 704230119165952
    m_Localized: Steuerung
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 704230886723584
    m_Localized: Relikte
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 704231637504000
    m_Localized: "Einf\xFChrung"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 704232384090112
    m_Localized: "Kost\xFCm & Spezial"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 704233143259136
    m_Localized: '- <COSTUME> changes your <BALL> visual and properties.

      Each
      <BALL> can only hold 1 <COSTUME>.

      - <SPECIAL> gives attached <BALL>
      a <UNIQUE> feature.

      Each <BALL> can only hold each <SPECIAL> once.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
